  "prompt": "What is the definition of dude?",
  "response": "\"Dude\" is an informal term typically used to refer to a person, often a man. It originated in the late 19th century as a slang word for a man who was overly concerned with his appearance and fashion, but over time, its meaning has broadened. Today, \"dude\" can be used to address or refer to a friend, acquaintance, or simply any person, regardless of gender. It is commonly used in casual conversation and is often associated with a laid-back or friendly tone.",
